<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1-3"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="4"/>roḷ niraṁtara dharmmavodala <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>ḷā viramanivārita satra varavidyādā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>namiṁtivaṁ māḍisidaṁ pa<unclear>la</unclear>vrikṣaṣō
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍasādi dvijavīthigaḷoḷaṁteyde mu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nnāda dharmma kuladharmma koḍe koṇḍa
<lb n="9"/>savasiya maḷeyakhēḍaṁ mahāgrāma
<lb n="10" break="no"/>meṁdaḍelepottu bijjesaypeṁ doreko
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḷa naṟugundaṁgaḷoḷtanna puṇyaṁ sale kēti mā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ḍidaṁ tārage himagiri caṁdrārkkaruḷḷa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nna menduṁ sāyamaputraṁ dharmmado
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ḷagā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kalitanadoḷa bhānujananni
</p>

